 Following her debut as the Love Island: Aftersun host, Maya, 28, wowed her followers on Instagram. Showing off her enviable curves in a figure-hugging bright pink dress, the television presenter gushed over her new favourite thing to do. She wrote in the caption: “Live TV is my absolute favourite. “First ever Aftersun show was so much fun (I was happier than I look in these posey pics lol ) - will be back every Sunday on ITV2.” with some red hearts. Maya is also fronting the new season of Love Island UK, breaking records as she became the first non-white host.